
Nuggeta GameServer is:

  * Fast
  * Free
  * Easy to use
  * Community Supported


Full documentation will be available soon at : http://developer.nuggeta.com/#!documentation



# Runtime Requirements
-----------------------

	* JAVA JDK :
		- install java Jdk 1.6 or greather : http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/index.html
		- set Environment variable JAVA_HOME point to the install directory. 
	* MONGODB : 
		- install mongoDB : http://www.mongodb.org/downloads , see install tutorial http://docs.mongodb.org/manual/tutorial/
		- start mongodb





# Run the GameServer
---------------------

	* For Windows :
		- go to bin folder and run the start.bat 
	* For Linux / MAC:
		- go to bin folder and run the command 'sh init.sh start' 
		
			
		
		

# Access the administration interface
-------------------------------------

	* open your browser to : http://localhost:9090
		
		
		
				
		
# Development Requirement
-------------------------

	* install Eclipse : http://www.eclipse.org/downloads
	* import the GameServer project
	* start develop your server logic !
		
	
	

